title: Congress' Benghazi probe not aimed at Clinton, lawmaker says
text:
Congress' Benghazi probe not aimed at... Congress' Benghazi probe not aimed at Clinton, lawmaker says There are 11 comments on the Reuters story from 11 hrs ago, titled Congress' Benghazi probe not aimed at Clinton, lawmaker says . In it, Reuters reports that: 
The Republican head of the congressional investigation into the Benghazi attack said on Sunday he is not targeting Democratic presidential front-runner Hillary Clinton and such talk hurts the inquiry. Clinton was secretary of state in September 2012 when U.S. facilities in Benghazi, Libya, were attacked, killing four Americans including U.S. Ambassador Christopher Stevens. Join the discussion below, or Read more at Reuters.
